<h2>3. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>

<h3>Why do I need an internet connection?</h3>
<p>
Airly may require an internet connection to load educational content, embedded videos,
and future updates that improve the app experience.
</p>

<h3>How can I give feedback or report a problem?</h3>
<p>
You can send an email to <strong>info@drakulastudios.com</strong> describing the issue or your suggestion.
We carefully review all feedback to improve the app.
</p>

<h3>Is my personal data safe?</h3>
<p>
Yes. Airly does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information.
All user data is stored locally on your device, as explained in our Privacy Policy.
</p>

